// bisect: MODE DIVERGENCE under fusion — soak jul06d (divergence_000000
// /000001, first catch of the extended generator: rec-in-fold COMPOSED
// with an error consumer). A deep tail-recursive `let rec` plus a
// try/catch (or checked-arith error-arm select) in the SAME fold
// callback: the error consumer splits the callback, the rec runs in
